[FILE] security.mdc
[OBJ] Security constraints.
[RULES]
1. [REQ] `[SEC-01]` Zero-trust validation. FormRequest/DTO for inputs.
2. [REQ] `[SEC-02]` Parameterized queries. No raw SQL interpolation.
3. [REQ] `[SEC-03]` Whitelist `$fillable`. No `$guarded = []`.
4. [REQ] `[SEC-04]` No PII/credentials in logs/commits.
5. [REQ] `[SEC-05]` Enforce RBAC (Filament Shield / policy gates).
6. [REQ] `[SEC-06]` Sanitize HTML outputs (DOMPurify).
7. [REQ] `[SEC-07]` Explicit DTO projections for client.
8. [REQ] `[SEC-08]` Encrypt at rest; private signed URLs.
9. [REQ] `[SEC-09]` API throttling & rate-limiting.
10. [REQ] `[SEC-10]` JWT in HttpOnly cookies. Regenerate session on login.
11. [PROHIBIT] No CORS wildcard `*`. No plaintext passwords. No internal traces in API.
